{"type": "article", "id": 12106, "title": "木制铜管小桌", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-15T11:03:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000038Si2z1FjKo5YcHbX9.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tSusana Piquer 设计了两款精巧的小桌子，桌面采用的是圆形或者方形的木板，而桌子腿则是使用的铜管，铜管交叉呈H形状，看上去非常简洁可爱。铜管和桌面的颜色搭配看上去十分干净，且形成材质上的相得益彰。桌面的形状可以按照个人喜好预定，<a href=\"http://cargocollective.com/susanapiquer\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看设计师个人主页。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135945MYKSxVh7ZQiF2PbI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261359462ZFgNHoC1dVbwJ0P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261359479dHlt4xOaP3geCST.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135947Ni6hl3uprvWPAHfV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}